Determine whether the computer needs to share files or printers


(Shows the current SMB server configuration)

Get-SmbServerConfiguration


(Enables and enforces SMB signing)

Set-SmbServerConfiguration -EnableSecuritySignature $true -RequireSecuritySignature $true -Confirm:$false


(Enables encryption of SMB traffic)

Set-SmbServerConfiguration -EncryptData $true -Confirm:$false


(Rejects SMB connections without encryption)

Set-SmbServerConfiguration -RejectUnencryptedAccess $true -Confirm:$false


(Disables the old SMB1 version)

Set-SmbServerConfiguration -EnableSMB1Protocol $false -Confirm:$false


(Lists currently shared SMB folders on the computer)

Get-SmbShare







